            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div role="main">
  
  <article>

    
<header>

  <div>

    <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PS5</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch-2">Switch 2</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a></li>    </ul>

    
    <p><span>Featuring Eiko Kano's Critikano Hit.</span>
      </p></div>

  

</header>  

<!-- Moved from templates/posts/default.php -->

    <div><p>Publisher and developer <a title="Companies > Square Enix [5,390 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/square-enix">Square Enix</a>, and developer <a title="Companies > Artdink Corporation [47 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/artdink-corporation">Artdink Corporation</a> premiered 37 minutes of live gameplay from <em><a title="Games > Dragon Quest I &amp; II HD-2D Remake [8 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/dragon-quest-i-ii-hd-2d-remake">Dragon Quest I &amp; II HD-2D Remake</a></em>‘s <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2025/09/dragon-quest-i-ii-hd-2d-remake-details-new-content-seabed">new seabed content</a> during a Tokyo Game Show 2025 stage event. <span id="more-996800"></span></p><p><em>Dragon Quest I &amp; II HD-2D Remake</em> is due out for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [10,502 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [8,006 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch 2 [523 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch-2">Switch 2</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch [17,763 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [24,401 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2893570/DRAGON_QUEST_I__II_HD2D_Remake/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a> and <a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/store/p/dragon-quest-i-ii-hd-2d-remake/9nf2kmv0rtpp" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Microsoft Store</a> on October 30. Read more about the game <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2025/05/dragon-quest-i-ii-hd-2d-remake-adds-switch-2-version-launches-october-30">here</a>, <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2025/07/dragon-quest-i-ii-hd-2d-remake-erdricks-legacy-trailer-latest-details">here</a>, <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2025/09/dragon-quest-i-ii-hd-2d-remake-gameplay-overview-trailer-scrolls-and-sigils-detailed">here</a>, and <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2025/09/dragon-quest-i-ii-hd-2d-remake-details-new-content-seabed">here</a>.</p><p>Watch the footage below.</p><h2><span>Gameplay</span></h2><p>(Gameplay footage from 23:04 to 1:00:17.)</p><!-- AD: content -->
