            <title><![CDATA[Dear me, I was… coming to Switch]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/09/dear-me-i-was-coming-to-switch</link>
            <guid>https://www.resetera.com/threads/dear-me-i-was%E2%80%A6-coming-to-switch.1310367/</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>

    <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a></li>    </ul>

    
    <p><span>Currently available for Switch 2.</span>
      </p></div><div><p><a title="Companies > Arc System Works [1,319 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/arc-system-works">Arc System Works</a> will release a <a title="Platforms > Switch [17,763 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a> version of interactive <a title="Genres > Adventure [2,599 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/adventure">adventure game</a> <em><a title="Games > Dear me, I was... [3 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/dear-me-i-was">Dear me, I was…</a></em>, the company <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=P9iQsDItvrs&amp;t=5221" target="_blank">announced</a>. A release date was not announced. <span id="more-996857"></span></p><p><em>Dear me, I was…</em> first launched for Switch 2 via <a href="https://store-jp.nintendo.com/item/software/D70010000099568" target="_blank">Nintendo eShop</a> on July 31.</p><p>In addition to the Switch version, Arc System Works has also released the game’s original soundtrack via streaming services like <a href="https://open.spotify.com/album/76bmAoKQ75CVEr3R9PnbVl" target="_blank">Spotify</a> and <a href="https://music.apple.com/us/album/dear-me-i-was-original-sound-track/1841855436" target="_blank">Apple Music</a>.</p><p>Here is an overview of the game, via Arc System Works:</p><blockquote><p><em>Dear me, I was…</em> is an interactive adventure that lets you enjoy a story woven with beautiful visuals, fusing the vibrant watercolor style of Taisuke Kanasaki with rotoscoping technology. The lifelike characters are sure to deeply move your heart.</p><p>In this story, you will relive the life of a certain woman. Experience joy, sorrow, and growth through her ordinary and humble life. Witness the story she weaves in a life interconnected with others.</p></blockquote><!-- AD: content -->
        </div></div><br/><br/>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/09/dear-me-i-was-coming-to-switch]]></content:encoded>
        </item>
