            <title><![CDATA[Monster Hunter Wilds x Final Fantasy XIV collaboration event quest ‘Planetes Protocol (Savage)’ announced]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/09/monster-hunter-wilds-x-final-fantasy-xiv-collaboration-event-quest-planetes-protocol-savage-announced</link>
            <guid>https://www.resetera.com/threads/monster-hunter-wilds-x-final-fantasy-xiv-collaboration-event-quest-%E2%80%98planetes-protocol-savage-%E2%80%99-announced.1310358/</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>

    <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PS5</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a></li>    </ul>

    
    <p><span>Available on September 29.</span>
      </p></div><div><p><a title="Companies > Capcom [2,627 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/capcom">Capcom</a> has announced the <em><a title="Games > Monster Hunter Wilds [40 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/monster-hunter-wilds">Monster Hunter Wilds</a></em> x <em><a title="Games > Final Fantasy XIV Online [8 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/final-fantasy-xiv-online">Final Fantasy XIV</a></em> speical collaboration permanent quest “Planetes Protocol.” It will become available on September 29. <span id="more-996789"></span></p><p>Here is an overview of the quest, via Capcom:</p><blockquote><p>For hunters seeking a true test of their skills, Omega Planetes offers an extreme challenge to those that have already proven their worth in the “Planetes Protocol” quest.</p><p>Introducing the high-difficulty, permanent quest, “Planetes Protocol (Savage).” Hunters that successfully fulfil their duty will earn materials to craft new weapons and armor unique to this challenging hunt, as well as being rewarded with a special pendant and gesture! </p></blockquote><p><em>Monster Hunter Wilds</em> is available now for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [10,502 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [8,006 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [24,401 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2246340/Monster_Hunter_Wilds/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a>.</p><p>Watch the announcement trailer below.</p><!-- AD: content -->
        <h2><span><em>Final Fantasy XIV</em> Special Collaboration: Planetes Protocol (Savage) <a title="Platforms > Quest [154 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/meta/quest">Quest</a> Reveal Trailer</span></h2><p><strong>English</strong></p><p><iframe title="MHWilds x Final Fantasy XIV Special Collaboration - Planetes Protocal (Savage) Quest Reveal" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/8JdNsvJknbY?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><p><strong>Japanese</strong></p><p><iframe title="「モンハンワイルズ×FF14」スペシャルコラボ | 超高難度イベントクエスト「零式オメガ・プラネテス検証戦」紹介映像" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ghBNahF2ICs?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p></div></div><br/><br/>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/09/monster-hunter-wilds-x-final-fantasy-xiv-collaboration-event-quest-planetes-protocol-savage-announced]]></content:encoded>
