    <p><span>An introduction to your home base.</span>
      </p></div><div><p>Publisher <a title="Companies > Konami Digital Entertainment [1,144 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/konami">Konami</a> and developer <a title="Companies > MYTHRIL [6 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/mythril">MYTHRIL</a> have released a new trailer for <em><a title="Games > Suikoden STAR LEAP [6 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/suikoden-star-leap">Suikoden STAR LEAP</a></em>, introducing the <a title="Genres > Free-to-Play [453 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/free-to-play">free-to-play</a> <a title="Genres > Strategy RPG [460 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/rpg/strategy-rpg">strategy RPG</a>‘s home base systems like hunts, the smithy, crests, mini-games (fishing, harvesting vegetables, mining, and so on), the suggestions box, dinner parties, and more. <span id="more-996781"></span></p><p><em>Suikoden STAR LEAP</em> will be available for <a title="Platforms > PC [24,401 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3668850/Suikoden_STAR_LEAP/" target="_blank">Steam</a>, iOS, and Android. A release date has yet to be announced.</p><p>Watch the trailer below.</p><h2><span>HQ Functions Trailer</span></h2><p><strong>Japanese</strong></p><p><iframe title="『幻想水滸伝 STAR LEAP』本拠地システムトレーラー" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/N-4g4Xduk5A?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><!-- AD: content -->
